    <h3 itemprop="headline">Permit obtained by AP shows schedule for Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce's wedding</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce's wedding is set to begin at New York's Madison Square Garden at 5 p.m. Friday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/07/02/permit-obtained-by-ap-shows-schedule-for-taylor-swift-and-travis-kelces-wedding/"  >(Jake Offenhartz, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
