    <h3 itemprop="headline">Finding freedom from the heat on July 4th will be a challenge in eastern US</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Gaining freedom from the heat will be a challenge this Independence Day in the eastern U.S., and it's already starting ahead of the holiday weekend.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/07/02/finding-freedom-from-the-heat-on-july-4th-will-be-a-challenge-in-eastern-us/"  >(Holly Ramer, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
