    <h3 itemprop="headline">Driver charged with manslaughter after Tesla crashes into Texas home, kills grandmother</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Ring doorbell footage shows the Tesla Model 3 slamming into a Katy, Texas, home at 73 mph while the DoorDash driver claims Full Self-Driving was engaged.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/07/03/driver-charged-manslaughter-tesla-crashes-texas-home-kills-grandmother/"  >(Fox News)</a>
