    <p itemprop="text">
      A Rhode Island airman missing since a secret World War II reconnaissance mission in 1944 has been identified through modern forensic testing.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/07/02/wwii-pilot-missing-secret-spy-mission-finally-accounted-80-years-later/"  >(Fox News)</a>
