    <h3 itemprop="headline">Couple charged with felonies for Empire State Building climb-turned-proposal</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Prosecutors say a skyscraper-scaling daredevil told police that he and his girlfriend climbed the Empire State Building’s antenna and unfurled a banner about love and peace because he wanted to “do something special” for their engagement.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/07/02/couple-charged-with-felonies-for-empire-state-building-climb-turned-proposal/"  >(Jennifer Peltz, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
