    <h3 itemprop="headline">Microsoft launches AI engineering company</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Microsoft has unveiled the Microsoft Frontier Company, a new operating business focused on delivering “frontier transformation” through AI for Microsoft’s customers around the world.
