        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Democratic governors press US Postal Service to drop plan tied to Trump's election order</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A group of Democratic governors is asking the U.S. Postal Service to withdraw its proposed rule to comply with an executive order that seeks to create a federal list of eligible voters, including those eligible to receive a ballot by mail.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/03/democratic-governors-press-us-postal-service-to-drop-plan-tied-to-trumps-election-order/"  >(Jesse Bedayn, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
