    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/07/02/republican-says-trumps-top-election-priority-dead-senate-gop-fractures-ahead-midterms.webp" alt="Republican says Trump's top election priority 'dead' in Senate as GOP fractures ahead of midterms" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Republican says Trump's top election priority 'dead' in Senate as GOP fractures ahead of midterms</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Sen. Thom Tillis says the SAVE America Act lacks the funding and time to be implemented before midterm elections, calling the push &quot;theater.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/02/republican-says-trumps-top-election-priority-dead-senate-gop-fractures-ahead-midterms/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 02 Jul 2026 12:45:29 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 02 Jul 2026 12:45:29 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Josh Boak, Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/07/02/trump-administration-proposes-a-rule-it-says-could-save-medicare-patients-11-billion-on-drugs.webp" alt="Trump administration proposes a rule it says could save Medicare patients $1.1 billion on drugs" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump administration proposes a rule it says could save Medicare patients $1.1 billion on drugs</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Trump administration is proposing a new rule to keep hospitals from marking up discounted drugs for Medicare patients.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/02/trump-administration-proposes-a-rule-it-says-could-save-medicare-patients-11-billion-on-drugs/"  >(Josh Boak, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
